00:15:35.720 --> 00:15:36.890 align:middle line:90%
of reality.

00:15:36.890 --> 00:15:41.140 align:middle line:84%
>> Yes, that's a very
nice point, Jeffrey.

00:15:41.140 --> 00:15:46.190 align:middle line:84%
The old Sanskrit practices
