00:16:02.310 --> 00:16:04.380 align:middle line:90%
>> It leads to abstractions.

00:16:04.380 --> 00:16:07.710 align:middle line:84%
>> It necessarily leads
to abstractions, yes.

00:16:07.710 --> 00:16:10.260 align:middle line:84%
Everything in physics
that's really fundamental

00:16:10.260 --> 00:16:12.690 align:middle line:90%
is abstract, like energy.

00:16:12.690 --> 00:16:15.450 align:middle line:90%
Energy is an abstraction.

00:16:15.450 --> 00:16:19.680 align:middle line:84%
Quantum numbers are
abstractions, quarks.

00:16:19.680 --> 00:16:23.700 align:middle line:84%
